comments: Vucevic (ORL) is firming up and absorbs the oncoming contact from Huerter (ATL) during the pick.
During the pick, Huerter (ATL) briefly places and arm on Ross's (ORL) side and removes it prior to his upward shooting motion.
Ross (ORL) moves through the lane and sets a screen on Gallinari (ATL), and the pair make marginal contact and disengage.
Vucevic (ORL) is firming up and makes marginal contact with Snell (ATL) as he sets the pick. Snell briefly places his arm on Vucevic's body as he fights over the pick.
Snell (ATL) establishes himself in a screening position in Carter-Williams' (ORL) path and the pair engage in arm to arm contact as they disengage.
Collins (ATL) is firming up and releases his arms into Carter-Williams (ORL) while disengaging from the pick.
Collins (ATL) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Aminu (ORL) that affects his shot at the rim.
Carter-Williams (ORL) makes contact with Young's (ATL) chin that affects his shot attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) and Gallinari (ATL) briefly engage and disengage.
Huerter (ATL) reaches across and brushes the ball on Ross's (ORL) drive to the basket and shot attempt, any additional contact to the arm is deemed incidental.
Carter-Williams (ORL) commits a take foul on Collins (ATL).
